I"S
<ol>
  <li>Noun(indicates time or distance) + ばかり(about, approximately)</li>
</ol>

<ul>
  <li>三時間ばかり歩いてから: walked for about three hours.</li>
</ul>

<ol>
  <li>verb-て form + ばかり(nothing but)
    <ul>
      <li>得るものはなく、失うものばかりだ: gain nothing, but everything to lose</li>
      <li>職場ではそんな話ばかり聞こえてくるぞ: that’s all I hear at work</li>
      <li>金、金、金。私、朝、昼、晩と金のことばかり考えてるよ: Money, I think about money all day.</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
</ol>

